{"tid":1168982,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔尿道造口手術","createTime":"2019-05-24T05:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:38.000Z","uid":219933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d4a5f866b8920dede0ab65ea6e4a8ea05c4aad","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"有無人嘅貓仔做過呢個手術呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n風險大唔大呀？<br />\n住院導尿導咗五日，都仲係屙唔到尿<br />\n照完超聲波話膀肛無沙石 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1845279aa988f1441d2d044c8e508df6c418d8eb","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"插唔到尿喉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e848b843eda5c1d99604b7ae3f783d809128f5f","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1845279aa988f1441d2d044c8e508df6c418d8eb","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"插唔到尿喉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"插到呀，不過feel到有一段收窄咗<br />\n同埋拆喉後都係屙唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb60bc7001f425de74c3abae86867f243e15152","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e848b843eda5c1d99604b7ae3f783d809128f5f","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1845279aa988f1441d2d044c8e508df6c418d8eb","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"插唔到尿喉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"插到呀，不過feel到有一段收窄咗<br />\n同埋拆喉後都係屙唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"下 屙唔到尿會中尿毒㗎喎 <br />\n醫生有冇話點解有一段收窄咗？<br />\n我隻貓仔都插過兩次尿喉 醫生話再有下次就要做造口手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9efea82d3bea87a20536ef63ebdc55ccddf659e","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb60bc7001f425de74c3abae86867f243e15152","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e848b843eda5c1d99604b7ae3f783d809128f5f","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1845279aa988f1441d2d044c8e508df6c418d8eb","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"插唔到尿喉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"插到呀，不過feel到有一段收窄咗<br />\n同埋拆喉後都係屙唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"下 屙唔到尿會中尿毒㗎喎 <br />\n醫生有冇話點解有一段收窄咗？<br />\n我隻貓仔都插過兩次尿喉 醫生話再有下次就要做造口手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T19:48:16.000Z","msg":"所以而家仲住緊院插尿喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫生話可能因為佢之前發過幾次炎，有可能纖維化咗（好似結咗焦咁）所以窄咗<br />\n或者都有可能佢天生窄啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd0606a7d33c29207191f9e2ea8e9d40d8933ff","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:29:01.000Z","msg":"插咗咁耐尿喉一定好辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我之前上網睇過造口手術即係變性手術，好大風險，個傷口容易爆開同發炎。<br />\n我隻貓睇開果個獸醫就話係救命手術嚟，如非必要都唔做。<br />\n你個獸醫點講？"},{"pid":"096f412b50aadbeae2afed860d4e3725afbfbf80","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd0606a7d33c29207191f9e2ea8e9d40d8933ff","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:29:01.000Z","msg":"插咗咁耐尿喉一定好辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我之前上網睇過造口手術即係變性手術，好大風險，個傷口容易爆開同發炎。<br />\n我隻貓睇開果個獸醫就話係救命手術嚟，如非必要都唔做。<br />\n你個獸醫點講？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"問咗2個獸醫，我嗰個話風險唔大；我朋友睇開嗰個話如果醫生做開，就風險好低<br />\n<br />\n朋友獸醫話，我貓貓已經試過幾次，建議做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5974cde660747844e026081c576c169949c269","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"096f412b50aadbeae2afed860d4e3725afbfbf80","tid":1168982,"uid":219933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdd0606a7d33c29207191f9e2ea8e9d40d8933ff","tid":1168982,"uid":149556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:29:01.000Z","msg":"插咗咁耐尿喉一定好辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我之前上網睇過造口手術即係變性手術，好大風險，個傷口容易爆開同發炎。<br />\n我隻貓睇開果個獸醫就話係救命手術嚟，如非必要都唔做。<br />\n你個獸醫點講？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"問咗2個獸醫，我嗰個話風險唔大；我朋友睇開嗰個話如果醫生做開，就風險好低<br />\n<br />\n朋友獸醫話，我貓貓已經試過幾次，建議做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"